{"tid":590344,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《幻影死神》再度製作TV動畫，2018年放送","createTime":"2018-03-12T14:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T06:49:42.000Z","uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4572fb202ce16abac28cb0aed4bbde5937783431","tid":590344,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/220017_aae465eb97634543d58a0ca86f06fb25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F220017_aae465eb97634543d58a0ca86f06fb25.jpg&h=d211e969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在3月10日的電擊文庫新作發布會活動上，1998年推出的小說《幻影死神》宣布將會再度製作TV動畫，而且還是由Madhouse負責製作。<br />\n<br />\n《幻影死神》是第4屆「電擊遊戲小說大獎」的獲獎作品，也是上遠野浩平（西尾維新與奈須蘑菇都表示受到過上遠野浩平的作品影響）的《ブギーポップシリーズ》小說第一作。在2000年這部小說就已經由Madhouse推出了全12話的TV動畫，同年還推出了真人電影。<br />\n<br />\n【STAFF】<br />\n監督：夏目真悟<br />\n系列構成：鈴木智尋<br />\n角色設計：澤田英彥<br />\n動畫製作：Madhouse<br />\n<br />\n【CAST】<br />\n宮下藤花：悠木碧<br />\n霧間凪：大西沙織<br />\n<br />\nsource: hkacger<br />\n<br />\n呢排Madhouse轉咗性? 係咁出續作嘅"},{"pid":"4ac8a647cb273cf1a935144cc79b83d501b12eac","tid":590344,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:29:38.000Z","msg":"其實冇咩睇過 2000年既動畫版<br />\n好多人都係公佈再動畫化先知動畫化過"},{"pid":"334f1393ce20bbe0eaa7a65a06e7a484e7747057","tid":590344,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:30:49.000Z","msg":"係時候補番"},{"pid":"c181a1d61dbfc0f9b9392c9131d914a98bbe8a31","tid":590344,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:33:20.000Z","msg":"當年套野電波到<br />\n賣碟得500銷量"},{"pid":"b3297d635aaf72926e94d415640a291c53a8ffc1","tid":590344,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"334f1393ce20bbe0eaa7a65a06e7a484e7747057","tid":590344,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:30:49.000Z","msg":"係時候補番"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"冇耐性，真係唔建議<br />\n套野係小說後日談性質，集集都係未講完既單元故事，又互相連接<br />\n要睇哂先會知套野講咩"},{"pid":"3eaf1b46f088d99d5f1e4d411ea636232abcca5a","tid":590344,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ac8a647cb273cf1a935144cc79b83d501b12eac","tid":590344,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:29:38.000Z","msg":"其實冇咩睇過 2000年既動畫版<br />\n好多人都係公佈再動畫化先知動畫化過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:38:05.000Z","msg":"唔講真係唔知有套咁嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361a3fdfe701eb28f81a709aea3ebca64167c3d2","tid":590344,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:38:29.000Z","msg":"同埋分鏡、用色、作畫<br />\n我都覺得幾差吓"},{"pid":"00a25c405e8c739a1dfc5c2e588a102f46f0874a","tid":590344,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3eaf1b46f088d99d5f1e4d411ea636232abcca5a","tid":590344,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ac8a647cb273cf1a935144cc79b83d501b12eac","tid":590344,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:29:38.000Z","msg":"其實冇咩睇過 2000年既動畫版<br />\n好多人都係公佈再動畫化先知動畫化過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:38:05.000Z","msg":"唔講真係唔知有套咁嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:47:05.000Z","msg":"不過公佈果日，成個twitter 講左成日<br />\n套野係世界系作品始祖、係到依家仲有新書出緊<br />\n<br />\n不吉波普不笑》被稱為「世界系作品的源頭」，據說奈須蘑菇和西尾維新都受到了這部作品的影響，雖說是97年的老作品，可是讀起來卻意外地沒有時代感哦。"},{"pid":"7cad848838a8b9ad2405f7de3a6fc6e0f0d9913c","tid":590344,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:49:42.000Z","msg":"套野當年係能登出道作"}]}